name: Something Evil : Sasquatch
description: You wake up in the forest. It is dark. Your camping buddies were with you only a few moments ago but they are nowhere to be seen. It is dark. And eerily quiet. The silence calms you. But then you hear it: a distant noise of branches breaking. Your eyes are not yet adjusted to the darkness. The noise is getting louder and louder. Something is approaching. My buddies are here, you think to yourself. And then a thunder strikes. Blinding. You open your eyes and you can barely see a silhouette. Something is here. And then you see it, standing right next to you. Eyes red, still, unblinking. Something...evil.
